{"tid":238032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人分享一個玩電話經歷","createTime":"2017-05-10T18:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T21:34:55.000Z","uid":23151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c6634f0877f87fe78f897ec179b342134737bb","tid":238032,"uid":23151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:45:10.000Z","msg":"個陣小學成日玩電話 ，諗番起都覺得好好笑（雖然俾人玩條友好慘）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就好小兒科，得閒打去81028332同埋打俾青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想聽下巴絲細個有咩好笑既玩電話經歷，分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5487742ee7b243473986eca8025c501a2ddb07","tid":238032,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:51:43.000Z","msg":"試過133打俾老師唔出聲:「喂.....喂.......」<br />\n133打俾親戚:「喂.....喂.......妖！」"},{"pid":"f4b89386baf664dad9d49330c1f9d6078c15d248","tid":238032,"uid":7843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:13:38.000Z","msg":"玩人就好少<br />\n<br />\n不過記得有一次細細個有個德國親人打長途電話返香港搵我呀媽，當時我呀哥聽左個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話聽唔到把聲又沙沙聲咁佢以為有人玩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢講左一聲「屌你老母玩電話」收左佢線<br />\n之後比老母屌到佢飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdf868f720af622dd37c5284776b822f5298286","tid":238032,"uid":69877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T21:34:55.000Z","msg":"記得細個試過打去傳說中唔打得既電話<br />\n唔記得係00000000定係咩<br />\n但一打到去有把恐怖聲<br />\n嚇撚到我即刻收線"}]}